    dc:description "FIG. 17. — Pedumispora rhizophorae K.D.Hyde & E.B.G.Jones (BRIP 19201 – holotype): A, herbarium material; B, C, appearance of ascostromata on host; D, section through ascoma; E, section through neck region; F, peridium; G, paraphyses; H, I, asci; J, K, ascospores. Scale bars: B, 1000 μm; C, 500 μm; D, 50 μm; E-G, 20 μm; H-K, 100 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7815093/files/figure.png" ;
